right after

1. *Ovoj* ključ mi je ukrao nepoznati čovek. (This key was stolen from me by an unknown man.)
2. Ona je uzela *ovoj* časopis. (She took this magazine.)
3. U *ovom* restoranu je fantastična hrana. (The food in this restaurant is fantastic.)
4. *Ovaj* film je veoma interesantan. (This movie is very interesting.)
5. Ona je došla na *ovu* proslavu. (She came to this celebration.)